strings: <voice_0x01001753><se_high>Media princess: Many thanks <hero> We look forward to your continued support.
<voice_0x01001754><se_high>Media princess: You help me when I need it
<voice_0x01001755><se_high>Media princess: But we tried it last time. I had to learn to take care of myself.
<voice_0x01001756><se_high>Media princess: Also, I can't leave you forever...
<voice_0x01001757><se_high>Media princess: Captain, you will be free soon! Available at the direct request of your daughter.
<voice_0x0100175A><se_high>Media princess: If you follow your dreams, you can live a decent life.
<voice_0x0100175B><se_high>Media princess: Hehe, I know you guys very well... but we grew up together.
<voice_0x0100175C><se_high>Media princess: Does anyone need you right now?
<voice_0x0100175D><se_high>Media princess: What do you think about it?
<voice_0x0100175E><se_high>Media princess: I also want to register
<voice_0x0100175F><se_high>Media princess: From now on, you will be a guardian.
<voice_0x01001760><se_high>Media princess: I wish you the best.
<voice_0x01001762><se_high>Media princess: It's time to listen to your heart and not give up on life.
<voice_0x01001763><se_high>Media princess: I am very happy to know that...
<voice_0x01001764><se_high>Media princess: I'm glad to meet you
